                                "start": 726.355,
                                "stop": 732.27,
                                "byte_start": 3008867,
                                "byte_stop": 3032586,
                                "text": "They -- they are -- are provisioned with respect to Legal Aid Society of the Bar Association, yes, sir."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 732.27,
                                "stop": 737.441,
                                "byte_start": 3032586,
                                "byte_stop": 3053275,
                                "text": "They are general provisions that apply to everybody that falls within them."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
